6 ADMINISTRATION OF THE VAPOR PRODUCTS TAX; PROVIDING PENALTIES; PROVIDING FOR
7 DISTRIBUTION OF REVENUE TO THE MEDICAID RESERVE ACCOUNT; PROVIDING AN
8 APPROPRIATION; PROVIDING RULEMAKING AUTHORITY; PROVIDING A DEFINITION DEFINITIONS;
9 AMENDING SECTION SECTIONS 16-11-102, AND 16-11-111 SECTION 53-6-151, MCA; AND PROVIDING
