16 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Incorporation by reference of tobacco product provisions -- license
17 requirement -- liability -- penalty. (1) Every wholesaler, subjobber, retailer, or vapor product vendor shall
18 obtain a license from the department and pay a license fee before engaging in the business in the same
